{"TopicId":213321,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Custom Flag Support","CreatedByName":"CyberSiren","CreatedById":226504,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T19:04:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"CyberSiren","CreatedById":226504,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T19:04:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstead of having to dig through Windows Explorer, or guess what resolution files are supposed to be, it would be nice if there settings to change your flag and have the game let you browse your local PC for image files to set as your flag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know its a long-shot, but the a cool solution to this would be having VERY SIMPLE \u0022Microsoft Paint\u0022 editor built into the game that allows players to use simple shapes and colors to design their own custom flag in-game. This would make peoples space agencies feel UNIQUE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-26T19:05:17Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2023 07:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by CyberSiren\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hecatonichosachoron","CreatedById":84257,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T19:56:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you actually found that folder? I\u0027d love to know where it is\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CyberSiren","CreatedById":226504,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T22:21:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224244742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022213321\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677441369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002284257\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hecatonichosachoron\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/26/2023 at 1:56 PM, Hecatonichosachoron said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you actually found that folder? I\u0027d love to know where it is\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood point. I haven\u0027t looked yet for it I just noticed there were no easy options in the in-game UI. I guess there isn\u0027t even a folder that we can access yet to edit them.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOtherDave","CreatedById":32305,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T23:43:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224244742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022213321\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677441369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002284257\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hecatonichosachoron\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/26/2023 at 11:56 AM, Hecatonichosachoron said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you actually found that folder? I\u0027d love to know where it is\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think I remember someone saying that the flags are all Unity assets for now, which, if true, probably makes custom flags at least difficult, if not impossible. I \u003Cem\u003Ethink\u003C/em\u003E custom flags was one of the things the devs have said is coming, so personally I probably wouldn\u0027t bother trying to hack them in now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hecatonichosachoron","CreatedById":84257,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-28T00:36:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a mod for it:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022189143\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1171432500\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/213372-fixes-and-mods-for-ksp-2/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022OGwOGpF.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/OGwOGpF.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlag material could stand to have less specular\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-28T00:37:44Z\u0022 title=\u002202/28/2023 12:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 28, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Hecatonichosachoron\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}